you need to install two 
-- PrimeNg and font-awesome

AngularCLI.json ==> this file tells the cli to which external style sheet to bundle 
finally for the application. 
add primeng and font-awesome stylesheets here..
The order is important ..so first add primeng and font-awesome stylesheets before the styles.css 

Themes: defines how they look 
you can change the theme with the avialable list of themes ...
once you find the theme , you need to add that theme to the styles array in angular.json 
you can find the themes under node_modules/resources/themes/bootstrap/ theme.css....

